title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 2 categories of Award on the x axis representing 2 groups: White, and Other Ethnicities.
Averaging the 2 groups, the highest category is found for Award Best Actor with a mean value of 50.0.
The minimum category is found at Best Actress with a mean value of 50.0.
In case of Best Actress, White shows more dominance than any other Award with a value 989.0 and it has the lowest value 932.0 in Best Actor.
